###

### Get all cohorts
GET http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Create new cohort
POST http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Cohort",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.png"
}

###

### Get cohort by ID
GET http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Update cohort
PUT http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Cohort Name",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/updated-image.png"
}

###

### Delete cohort
DELETE http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Add user to cohort
POST http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Remove user from cohort
DELETE http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get cohort users
GET http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get chat messages
GET http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}/chat/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get leaderboard
GET http://localhost:5082/api/cohorts/{{cohortId}}/leaderboard
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get current user profile
GET http://localhost:5082/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Update user profile
PUT http://localhost:5082/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updateduser",
  "email": "updateduser@example.com",
  "profilePicture": "https://example.com/newpic.png"
}